title: Akira Kurosawa-Stray Dog (1949)
description:
During a sweltering summer, Murukami, a young homicide detective, has his pocket picked on a bus and loses his Colt pistol. Frantic and ashamed, he dashes about trying to recover the weapon without success until taken under the wing of an older and wiser detective, Sato. Together they track the culprit.
